Singer Polina Gagarina named helping to lose weight products
Russian singer Polina Gagarina named five foods that helped her adjust the figure and subsequently not gain weight again.
The first on the list was water.
The singer prefers to drink clean ungassed water before each meal to quench her hunger and eat less.
Also, vegetable salad, brown rice and seafood are ideal for maintaining slimness.
Thanks to them, you can make a balanced diet: vegetables contain fiber, rice contains complex carbohydrates, and seafood is a source of protein, useful vitamins and amino acids.
For unloading days, the singer chooses apples.
Thanks to these products Gagarina was able to get rid of 30 extra kilograms.
In addition, the singer switched to a fractional diet - eating often and little by little and excluded from the diet fat, sweet and calorie.
Gagarina does not eat fried food, baked goods, sausages and other meat semi-finished products, writes kp.ru on July 26.
It has also replaced red meat with fish and seafood.
Prefers vegetables (except potatoes), whole grains and lots of greens.
Also Gagarina is actively engaged in the gym, yoga and running.
